<br>
Ears - Forest Loop - Cost under 500 and at your level you can get these by grouping at the Giant Fort in Frontier Mountains.<br>
Head - Runed Circlet - Cost under 300 - You can get this at your level in Permafrost<br>
Bracers - Runed Mithril Bracelet - Cost under 500<br>
Shoulders - Braided Ivy Cords - Cost under 400<br>
Back - Mammoth Hide Cloak - Cost under 1k - You can get this at your level in Permafrost<br>
Legs - Gatorscale Leggings - Cost under 1k - You can get these in upper guk<br>
<br>
